Mortimer: Hello. I would need a potion to [color={bold_color}]incapacitate people[/color]. Or make sure they don't have a good time. Can I count on you to help me out?

Mortimer: Thank you. I'll be back in [color={bold_color}]2 days[/color] to pick it up.

set {request} = "Laxative potion. Please"
set {deadline} = 2.0
